Class DatabaseInputNoLearner

  • java.lang.Object
    • semanticMarkup.ling.learn.lib.PerlTerminologyLearner
      • semanticMarkup.ling.learn.lib.DatabaseInputNoLearner
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ITerminologyLearner

    public class DatabaseInputNoLearner
extends PerlTerminologyLearner
    DatabaseInputNoLearner does not learn actively itself but reads the results of a learn process of the e.g. the previous charaparser perl part, or PerlTerminologyLearner from the database.
    Author:
    rodenhausen
